title: Oops — Nvidia has just accidentally revealed a brand new GPU
description: A new demo of Nvidia Reflex in Counter-Strike 2 reveals a GPU that has already been the subject of much speculation.

title: Google Earth updates cool Timelapse feature with new imagery
description: Google Earth has updated its Timelapse feature with new imagery from 2021 and 2022, so you can now watch changes to the landscape unfold across four decades.
